## Understanding RV Insurance

RV insurance protects your recreational vehicle investment from accidents, theft, weather damage, and liability claims. Unlike auto insurance, RV policies must account for your vehicle's dual nature as both transportation and living space.

### Types of RVs and Insurance Considerations

| RV Type | Value Range | Insurance Cost Range | Key Coverage Needs |
